WEBVTT

37:02.760 --> 37:04.360 line:80%
But after they took him home,

37:04.430 --> 37:06.090 line:80%
he died suddenly in the night.

37:06.350 --> 37:07.510 line:80%
Early this morning,

37:07.510 --> 37:09.640 line:80%
they brought a coffin to the door
and made a scene,

37:09.640 --> 37:11.680 line:80%
demanding we pay for the old man's death.
